    "eyebrow": "Group Discussion",
    "num": "19",
    "deck": "<div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"eyebrow anim\"><span class=\"num\">19</span><span class=\"bar\"></span>Group Discussion</div><h2 class=\"head anim\">Cultural Blending and Conflicts Among Texicans</h2><ul><li>Texican identity emerged from Mexican and Anglo cultural fusion</li><li>Conflicts arose over language, religion, and governance</li><li>Shared experiences forged a distinct Texican community</li></ul><p class=\"lede anim\">Texican culture was dynamic and sometimes conflicted, reflecting the challenges of blending diverse traditions under Mexican rule. <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s7\">[7]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s8\">[8]</sup></p><div class=\"lesson-detail anim\"><p><strong>Example:</strong> Disputes over language use in government and schools exemplify cultural tensions.</p><p><strong>Practice:</strong> Discuss how cultural blending both united and divided Texicans.</p><p><strong>Watch for:</strong> Assuming cultural blending eliminated all conflicts.</p></div></div>",
